<cell id="cell-0"><cell_type>markdown</cell_type># Lab 3.1 — Embeddings + cosine from scratch
20-line numpy cosine, then embed-english-v3.0, then a 2D PCA plot.
Cost: ~$0.02 (Cohere embed-english-v3.0 at $0.10/1M; ~200K tokens for the 100-paper corpus).</cell id="cell-0">
<cell id="cell-1">!uv add numpy cohere scikit-learn matplotlib</cell id="cell-1">
<cell id="cell-2">import numpy as np
def cosine(a, b):
    return float(a @ b / (np.linalg.norm(a) * np.linalg.norm(b)))
docs = np.array([[1,0.1,0,0],[0.9,0.2,0,0],[0,0,1,0.1]], dtype=float)
q = np.array([1.0,0,0,0])
for i,d in enumerate(docs): print(f"doc{i}: {cosine(q,d):.3f}")</cell id="cell-2">
<cell id="cell-3">import os, cohere
assert os.environ.get("COHERE_API_KEY"), "set COHERE_API_KEY (free tier)"
co = cohere.Client(api_key=os.environ["COHERE_API_KEY"])
titles = ["Attention Is All You Need","BERT: Pre-training of Deep Bidirectional Transformers",
         "A Simple Framework for Contrastive Learning","High-Resolution Image Synthesis with Latent Diffusion",
         "Language Models are Few-Shot Learners"]
E = np.array(co.embed(texts=titles, model="embed-english-v3.0", input_type="search_document").embeddings)
E /= np.linalg.norm(E, axis=1, keepdims=True)
print(np.round(E @ E.T, 2))</cell id="cell-3">
<cell id="cell-4">from sklearn.decomposition import PCA
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
xy = PCA(n_components=2).fit_transform(E)
for (x,y), t in zip(xy, titles):
    plt.scatter(x,y); plt.annotate(t[:30], (x,y), fontsize=7)
plt.title("embed-english-v3.0 title embeddings, PCA to 2D"); plt.show()</cell id="cell-4">
<cell id="cell-5"># Asymmetric encoding gotcha — run this and watch sims drop
q_emb = np.array(co.embed(texts=["transformer attention mechanism"], model="embed-english-v3.0", input_type="search_query").embeddings[0])
q_emb /= np.linalg.norm(q_emb)
d_as_doc = co.embed(texts=["transformer attention mechanism"], model="embed-english-v3.0", input_type="search_document").embeddings[0]
d_as_doc = np.array(d_as_doc); d_as_doc /= np.linalg.norm(d_as_doc)
print(f"query-vs-same-text-as-doc: {cosine(q_emb, d_as_doc):.3f}")
print(f"query-vs-same-text-as-query: {cosine(q_emb, q_emb):.3f}")</cell id="cell-5">